docs.lead_paragraph: The Injuction on Mayor Lambert 'Extra Salary. A motion made by ex-Judge DIKEMAN in Special Term, (Brooklyn,) yesterday morning, to continue this injunction (granted temporarily on the 27th of December, and since then continued by adjournment and consent,) until the final determination and judgment in the action, was unopposed by the Corporation Council and granted by the Court.

DICK TINTO ON HIS TRAVELS.; Leghorn--Off and In--Its Inhabitants--What the City Was Once, and What it Now Is--Adventuies--Pantomime 'vice Language, &c.

docs.lead_paragraph: Leghorn--an uncouth corruption of Livorne, its musical Italian name-is not only the chief sea-port of Tuscany, but it is one of the most important in the Mediterranean. It lies in a low plain, which spreads outward for several miles, and behind which the Appenines rise in successful ridges, distinctly visible as you approach the town, and girding the whole eastern and southern horizon.
